<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我聽大家說<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />島上好像很快就會舉辦<delay8 />
第一場大型活動！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />我光是用想的，<delay8 />就覺得好興奮啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種期待的感覺，<delay20 />就像健身完
在等隔天肌肉痠痛的時候啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天終於就是這座島上<delay20 />
第一次舉辦活動的日子啦──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你做好<delay8 />心理準備了嗎？<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是已經做好<delay8 />隨時應對的萬全準備囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好耶！<delay8 />我開始熱血沸騰啦──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個星期六<delay8 />就是釣魚大會啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了這個大會，<delay8 />正在利用時間
進行秘密訓練喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我為了<delay20 />能夠長時間拿著釣竿，<delay8 />
正在針對肱二頭肌……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔唷，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不能再說下去啦──！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是<delay frames="16" />釣魚大會啦！
<tag a="110" b="3" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會向你展現<delay8 />我努力健身的成果，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你最好先做好心理準備喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這週的星期六<delay8 />就是捕蟲大會啦──！<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好了嗎？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在已經鍛鍊出<delay8 />
很精實的肱三頭肌囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />準備好見識<delay8 />我的捕蟲技術吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是捕蟲大會啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我已經開始心癢難耐啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但不是被蟲咬到的那種癢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天<delay8 />終於就是<delay20 />煙火大會啦——！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想到大會中不知道會有多少<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大型煙火射向空中，我就好興奮啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經<delay8 />準備好了嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？你還問我準備什麼？<delay20 />明天不就是
快樂家協會<delay8 />公布分數的日子嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想拿高分其實難度還挺高的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是，<delay8 />如果不拿出幹勁好好準備，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是得不到好成績的喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay20 />
你拿到的快樂家協會分數
是多少啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的話<tag a="110" b="0" />大致上來說，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該就是令人期待之後的成長吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過說起來，<delay8 />評審到底<delay20 />都是什麼時候，<delay8 />
來看房間的啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今年也要結束了耶──！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺時間過得真快！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來<delay8 />就等31日的跨年倒數活動到來！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />今年的最後一個慶典，<delay20 />
我們就一起盛大的慶祝吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等到明天，<tag a="90" b="27" />年也終於要結束了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好了嗎？<tag a="110" b="3" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上在廣場上會舉辦倒數活動，<delay20 />
我們就和大家一起熱鬧地慶祝吧！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到最後<delay8 />都不要鬆懈喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我跟你說，<delay8 />已經快要5月1號了，<delay20 />
也就是說勞動節已經快到啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說好像會在其他島上舉辦活動喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />到底會是什麼樣的活動啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人好奇耶——！<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">明天就是勞動節了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay8 />已經準備好了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要前往舉辦勞動節活動的<tag a="110" b="32" />，<delay8 />
就必須要有<colour id="1" />勞動節旅行券<colour id="65535" />喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />應該會知道<delay8 />活動的詳細內容，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天要記得去<colour id="1" />服務處<colour id="65535" />喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />
你知道10月31日是什麼日子嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay8 />就是讓人期待已久的萬聖節——！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到萬聖節的事前準備，那就是糖果啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為大家都很想要糖果，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以得多準備一點才行喔——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是萬聖節啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經做好萬全準備啦——！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了這一天，<delay20 />我準備了一套<delay8 />
很特別的服裝喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />是不是開始期待啦？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
感恩節馬上就要到了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經<delay8 />迫不及待當天的到來啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想到擺滿佳餚的廣場，<delay20 />
就讓人興奮不已對吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />糟糕，我的口水流出來了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是感恩節啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經做好過節準備啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是去廣場享用料理，<delay frames="30" />
或者是在家做料理。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管怎樣，<delay20 />我都會吃得飽飽的。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也趁現在<delay20 />先把肚子的
空間空出來吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay20 />你注意到了嗎？<delay frames="30" />
平安夜的腳步已經很近了喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />禮物該送什麼才好啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />我不太擅長包裝啊……<delay20 />
得在節日到來前好好練習一下才行。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想想，<delay8 />不管禮物的內容物是什麼，<delay20 />
只要包裝包得好看，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來就會很豪華不是嗎！？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊——！<delay20 />
明天就是期待已久的平安夜囉！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕禮物也已經準備好了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得<delay20 />我會送什麼禮物啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你很在意的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在當天親眼確認看看吧——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>